<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Enterprise pricing opaque without sales call</li>
<li>Interface complexity requires training</li>
<li>Overkill for single-brand SMBs</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Verdict:</strong> Profound AI is the best LLM optimization tool for enterprise teams that need complete visibility across every major AI platform. The depth of data justifies the price for organizations where AI reputation carries material business risk.</p>
