<p><strong>Team size.</strong> Solo marketers and small teams should start with Otterly.AI or the free theStacc AI Visibility Checker. Mid-size teams benefit from Semrush or Ziptie. Enterprise teams need Profound, Scrunch, or Ahrefs Brand Radar.</p>
<p><strong>Budget.</strong> At $29 per month, Otterly.AI is the best value for teams under $10 million revenue. At $99 per month, Semrush offers the best feature-to-price ratio for teams already using the platform. At $295 per month, AthenaHQ is justified only for e-commerce brands that can attribute revenue to AI citations.</p>
<p><strong>Existing stack.</strong> If you use Semrush, the AI Visibility Toolkit is the natural choice. If you use Ahrefs, Brand Radar connects directly. If you use neither, Profound or Otterly offer standalone platforms that do not require existing subscriptions.</p>
<p><strong>Primary goal.</strong> If your goal is reputation monitoring, choose Profound or Otterly. If your goal is content optimization, choose Semrush or Scrunch. If your goal is revenue attribution, choose AthenaHQ. If your goal is competitive intelligence, choose Ahrefs Brand Radar.</p>
